phrases: This is my tenth consecutive win!
I will pass you the fish.
I-I am telling you, I can do it by myself...
Tension zings through the room even in an ordinary scene of domestic bliss.
Maybe... you can switch with Tsukiumi sometimes...
That position next to Minato rightfully belongs to me, his real wife!
Therefore, it is meaningful to get it back by my own hands!
Is not that a bit over the top?
It is a matter of my pride as thy real wife!
So, I will compete in the shopping race, too!
She is full of fighting spirit.
Kusano-tan's never really gone out of the house, and she may get lost,
or face something even more dangerous.
But looking at her, I fear she shall not listen to us,
no matter how hard we try to convince her.
Ku-chan always asks me what she can do to help me.
I wonder if because she is the littlest
that she wants to work as hard as everybody else does.
Well, I do rather understand her feelings.
But I worry about her going out shopping alone.
Then I will give her a hand.
Let us start the shopping race!
We will watch over her stealthily from the shadows
so she can succeed at shopping, will not we?
We shall put aside our duel this time.
Now I can pinpoint her position no matter where she goes!
It is kind of nice... that everybody's working hard for Ku-chan.
I am sure that they are good kids because you are the one they are with.
The landlady put the map in her shopping bag!
It seems like she is completely forgotten about the map.
Kusano-tan's straying from the planned path.
We do not need you to tell us that!
Ah, if you have a map, you should look at it.
I just blocked the road and told her about the map.
She calls this just blocking the road?
The shopping district is straight ahead.
She is going into the alley!
She looks like she is chasing Mr. Cat.
Hey Kusano, that is dan... dan...
She is off of her route again.
This is not the time for that!
If that is how you want to play this...
Why is Kusano-tan taking such a complicated route?
We can just lead Mr. Cat toward the shopping district.
She is getting close to the shopping district.
Supermarket Maruyama But... what are all these...
We managed to lead her to her destination...
All that is left is to buy potatoes and carrots.
Organic Vegetables Corner I wonder if she is forgotten what to get.
I wonder if she is forgotten what to get.
Why do I have to act so suspiciously?
Ah, this is the season when potatoes and carrots taste the best!
Those are absolutely the things to get.
Now, all she needs to do is go home.
Kusano-tan's made it home safe and sound!
Let our solemn duel begin now!
I have the superior sprinting power.
The seat next to Minato shall be mine!
You helped me a whole lot with my shopping, did not you?
Oh well, considering how flashy they were about it, it would be odd if she did not notice.
I could not shop by myself.
So I lost the shopping race.
No, the seat next to Minato belongs to thee.
Thou didst well in thy very first shopping trip.
Thou art certainly qualified to be his wife.
Out of respect, we have decided to grant thee a seat next to Minato forever.
Our plan was a complete failure.
We did it so secretly, too...
That lack of self-awareness might be the biggest because for this failure.
My, it is unusual for all three of you to be in the bath at once, is not it?
We are reviewing our game today while we wash up.
Ku-chan found out we were helping her behind the scenes.
But I think you were both admirable.
You gave her a seat next to Sahashi-san, did not you?
If our other choice is to worry this much each time...
It is much easier for us to just race by ourselves.
They are taking a bath so we can have dinner together after you wake up.
How about we all go out shopping together sometime?
I like Mu-chan, Tsu-chan, Ma-chan, and everybody very much!
